title: Camtasia.Studio.v8.4.1.Incl.Keygen-TSZ
description:

YCKCC-ZQCC4-UYCC9-CXW5A-D5MFA

These are provided for people who don't trust the keygen.
It doesn't matter what you use for the User-Name.
Use the cmd script to auto-add stuff to your hosts file.

The way the activation works is that it will let you
use the program while trying to verify the activation
in the background. If you block the communication with
the hosts file lines, it won't un-verify the serials.

To remove the 2 lines in your hosts file later, you will
need to copy the %windir%_system32_device_etc_hosts file
to another non-system directory such as your desktop. Then
modify it with a text editor such as notepad. Then copy/replace
it over the old one.

I have a family member who's new at video editing for youtube
and I figured I'd share the wealth since this is a fairly new
release of it.

Enjoy,
murph
